<LP>
   Baltimore Gas &amp; Electric Co., Baltimore, requested an
annual rate increase of 12.1% or $198 million in an
application filed with the Maryland Public Service
Commission.
   The increase requests includes $45 million, proposed as
the first part of a three-stage phase-in of revenues required
