<LP>
   Marriott Corp. said in Washington that it signed a
licensing agreement to develop 70 Nathan's Famous Inc.
fast-food restaurant units over the next five years.
   The first two outlets are scheduled to open in New York's
La Guardia Airport and the Neshaminy Travel Plaza on the
