   Financial terms weren't disclosed, but Marriott said the
agreement gives the lodging and food services company
exclusive development rights to the Nathan's Famous concept
at airports, travel plazas and certain food service
operations in the U.S. and Canada.
   Marriott said that, in preparation for the contract, it
operated two Nathan's Famous test sites last year on the
